  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Handling, checking, receiving, picking of goods</li>\n  <li>Ensure accuracy of goods description &amp; quantity upon put away in storage</li>\n  <li>Assist all sales orders had been picked &amp; processed by end of the day</li>\n  <li>Proper house keeping and maintaining of storage area</li>\n  <li>Perform any other duties as directed by supervisor from time to time</li>\n  <li>Other assigned ad-hoc duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Positive work attitude</li>\n  <li>Have good sense of responsibility</li>\n  <li>A good team player with a highly motivated team</li>\n  <li>Have good sense of responsibility</li>\n  <li><strong>Able to work in cold room environment</strong></li>\n</ul>",
